<subSubSection pageId="707" pageNumber="708" type="note">
<paragraph pageId="707" pageNumber="708">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="707" pageNumber="708">
Ball (1973: 74) proposed 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Ball" authorityYear="1973" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="707" pageNumber="708" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cunctipeps">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="707" pageNumber="708">Harpalus cunctipeps</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to replace 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Casey" baseAuthorityYear="1914" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="707" pageNumber="708" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="puncticeps">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="707" pageNumber="708">Harpalus puncticeps</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Casey, 1914), a junior secondary homonym of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Casey" baseAuthorityYear="1914" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="707" pageNumber="708" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="puncticeps">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="707" pageNumber="708">Harpalus puncticeps</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Stephens, 1828), both species being then placed in the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1802" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Harpalus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="707" pageNumber="708" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="707" pageNumber="708">Harpalus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Since 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Stephens’">Stephens'</normalizedToken>
species is currently included in the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1821" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Ophonus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="707" pageNumber="708" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="707" pageNumber="708">Ophonus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and the replacement name was proposed after 1960, the original species-group name is to be reinstated (ICZN 1999: Article 59.4).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
